  "content": "<div class=\"ql-editor read-mode\"><p><strong style=\"background-color: white; color: rgb(66, 66, 66);\">For Desktop:</strong><span style=\"background-color: white; color: rgb(66, 66, 66);\"> You can start </span><strong style=\"background-color: white; color: rgb(66, 66, 66);\">ePOS</strong><span style=\"background-color: white; color: rgb(66, 66, 66);\"> system by double click or right click on shortcut icon&nbsp;on your computer desktop (</span><em style=\"background-color: white; color: rgb(66, 66, 66);\">if you right click on icon then click Open</em><span style=\"background-color: white; color: rgb(66, 66, 66);\">).</span></p><p><img src=\"/files/5ZNMl3Q.png\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto;\" align=\"center\"></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: white; color: rgb(66, 66, 66);\">For Mobile:</strong><span style=\"background-color: white; color: rgb(66, 66, 66);\"> You can start </span><strong style=\"background-color: white; color: rgb(66, 66, 66);\">ePOS Mobile</strong><span style=\"background-color: white; color: rgb(66, 66, 66);\"> system by tab on shortcut icon on your mobile screen.</span></p><p><img src=\"/files/5GtiQGn.png\"></p></div>",
